data.meta_description: Cemetery in small yard in Hollywood for famous people. Image is of a large flat plaque that is the side of a burial plot. It is lying on the ground and is a dark red with golden writing and trim. There is a bouquet of white flowers at the head of it along with a bot of red flowers.
